{"tid":2203367,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男生去年11月集會藏噴漆今獲撤控准守行為","createTime":"2020-09-15T09:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T09:34:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"405db2ab73b014ebd24e90c607ad124d496ab687","tid":2203367,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"市民去年11月在中環分別參與獲發不反對通知書的《香港人權民主法案》集會，以及「和你摺紙鶴」活動，惟未幾遭警方腰斬，並發生警民衝突。一名17歲學生當晚在警員驅散示威者時被截停，搜出噴漆，事隔半年後被控管有物品意圖損壞財產罪。男生今獲撤控，以簽保守行為方式結案。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今表示，現已年滿18歲的被告年紀尚輕，要求法庭考慮判處守行為12個月，惟裁判官劉綺雲認為不合適。辯方聞言，表示希望守行為時間不要超過36個月。劉官最終批准被告自簽2,000元、守行為24個月，其間不得干犯或企圖干犯摧毀或損壞他人財產的罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/3Z6PDVQRJFCZ5BP5TPCNWJSAUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2F3Z6PDVQRJFCZ5BP5TPCNWJSAUQ%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuWlQkZRBUTTGMtnLt8L03NM%3D&h=ae702ec2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2F3Z6PDVQRJFCZ5BP5TPCNWJSAUQ%2F&h=133e96a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/3Z6PDVQRJFCZ5BP5TPCNWJSAUQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f17a6e323e3127658bba76da1d2ed7036c8dff59","tid":2203367,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T09:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9faf20e42101969879eb4bf17c1a054b8f8f1c0c","tid":2203367,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T09:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">====================<br />\n</